This directory is reserved for the pinned Polkadot SDK foundation.

The full SDK source is installed through the repository submodule configuration:

  git submodule update --init --recursive

Target upstream:

  https://github.com/paritytech/polkadot-sdk.git

Pinned upstream commit used for planning:

  bcafdb3d87eb3756f64bd1e830b0785d17a86812

SubReparo additions are kept outside the SDK tree for clarity and copied into the SDK workspace by:

  scripts/bootstrap-sdk-foundation.sh
  scripts/bootstrap-sdk-foundation.ps1
